title: Coffee consumption in the U.S. 2013/14 - 2018/19
summary: Overall Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags has increased over the Year.
Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags is slightly increasing from 2016/2017 to 2018/2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016/2017 and 2017/2018.
Maximum Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags, about 26.5 was reported at Year 2018/2019
The lowest Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags, of value 25.02 was reported at Year 2016/2017
